record.title: THE JOURNAL
record.chair: The Chair has examined the Journal of the last day's proceedings and announces to the House his approval thereof.

speaking-unknown-id.title: Mr.
speaking-unknown-id.name: SENSENBRENNER
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, pursuant to clause 1, rule I, I demand a vote on agreeing to the Speaker's approval of the Journal.

record.chair: The question is on the Speaker's approval of the Journal.

speaking-unknown-id.title: Mr.
speaking-unknown-id.name: SENSENBRENNER
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, on that I demand a division.

speaking-unknown-id.title: Mr.
speaking-unknown-id.name: HOYER
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, on that I demand the yeas and nays.

record.narrative: The yeas and nays were ordered.
record.chair: Pursuant to clause 8 of rule XX, further proceedings on this question will be postponed.
